comment_data.body:
Ternaries are borderline impossible to format because it violates the "inner expression indentation" rule from clint.

This question pops up pretty frequently. Should we just bite the bullet and remove the clint rule? Maybe uncrustify will gain the ability to do this in the future, if so we can start using that.

@bfredl

